Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This just got real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there so I've\Ngot a few things to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, who here besides\Nme thinks this is the best
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria Games delegation\Nin Ponyville history?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And no matter what\Nyour sport is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,we've gotta give it our best
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because we've all got a genuine\Nshot at Ponyville gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With the possible\Nexception of Bulk Biceps,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we're good and all, but\Nwe're up against the Wonderbolts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the aerial relay, so\Ngold's kind of a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not kid ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel bad, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have absolutely no shot\Nat winning gold, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, that's because you're\Ncarrying the flag for Ponyville
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in the opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Winners or not, we still have\Nthe chance to be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that, everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Winners or not, we all still\Nhave the chance to be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But uh, let's\Nstill try to win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,lots and lots of stuff too, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! It's all in there, gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to Spike,\Nchampion gear carrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for all your\Ngear-carrying needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Ponyville flag?\NYou sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about the flagpole?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.61,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,In with the portable ramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest,\NApplebloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw she's just nervous,\Nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfectly understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I'm afraid I'll forget\Nsomething and I start to panic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a simple\Ntrick: I count to ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the time I'm done,\NI've calmed myself enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to get the job done\Nright every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy peasy cider squeezy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Are you\Nall right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A thousand pardons, O\NGreat and Honorable Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for bringing\NSpike to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have our hoofponies\Ngo back for your bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they hang back a sec and\Ntell me what's going on first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ponies here think\NI'm some kind of hero, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,More of the green ones, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the green ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last time you were here,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you got the Crystal Heart\Nto Princess Cadance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in time to save this entire\Nempire from destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You are known\Nthroughout my empire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as Great and Honorable\NSpike the Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a big shot here, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why we all hope\Nyou'd do us the honor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of lighting the torch at\Nthe opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be the very\Nfirst dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,in the history of the\NEquestria Games to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And bonus: I can do it\Nwith my fire breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Places for the\Nprocession, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're quite certain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you also understand exactly what\Nyou're supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I stand where you tell me\Nuntil you give me the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I walk over\Nand light the torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. Couldn't be simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. The Dragon? Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Would somepony help him walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now please welcome the\Ndelegation from Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville forever! YAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,yay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you the signal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. The Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Count to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, thousand,\Nfourteen thousand,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,twenty thousand,\Nthirty thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me this isn't happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Equestria, we\Nhave a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. The Dragon, would you\Nlight the torch already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is, but I\Njust don't have the stuff today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fire-breathing dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then some cough drops, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony go down and help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah well, better\Nlate than never.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the Games begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! There are our\Nlittle superstars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You were fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Made me sit up proud like\Na cornstalk in August.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya done good, squirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You three\Nreally were wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But does anypony know what\Nwas going on with Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure seemed to be havin'\Na tough time of it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He put things right\Nin time, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want him\Nto be embarrassed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so I cast a secret spell\Nto light it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear. Have you\Ntold him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but he might have\Nfigured it out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta tell him just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I'm just afraid\Nof how he'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what pride he\Ntakes in a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Psst. Here he\Ncomes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Act casual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Is everything OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The weirdest thing\Nhappened down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, about that. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there I was,\Ntrying to light the torch,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,with all of Equestria watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and feeling like the\Nhugest failure ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the thing just\Nlit. It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Phew! I was afraid\Nyou'd be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Upset? Are you kidding? Why\Nwould I be upset to discover
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can light fire with my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's the Great\Nand Honorable Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the Brave and Glorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How you saved our empire\Nlast time you were here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,was really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw. You know what\Nelse is amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Once it bursts\Ninto flames through brainpower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sign another one\Nfor you. Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, may I have\Na word with you a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Better be careful with that.\NMight burst into flames later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Delayed reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Twi, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, hold on!\NGive me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can set fire to\Nstuff with my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,mindreading must be\Njust around the corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I predict that you\Nare about to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to set fire to something\Nwith my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Because you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really? So how do you explain\Nwhat happened down there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of thousands\Nand thousands--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, Spike. I cast a\Nspell to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,... in front of thousands\Nand thousands...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stand to\Nsee you stuck like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...I need to be\Nalone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O Great and Honorable Spike\Nthe Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You should probably\Nask somebody special instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our next event:{\i0}\N{\i1}the aerial relay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Dash and Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, we can't\Nbe late for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, step right over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unicorns will no{\i0}\N{\i1}longer be admitted{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without a disabling spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To prevent cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And make sure you don't\Neven try casting a spell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or we'll know it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ponyville medals here\Nwe'll have 8 medals so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,putting us tied for the\Nlead with Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless Cloudsdale\Nmedals here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Harshwhinny, I know\Nyou're really busy but--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's something else I\Ncan do for the Games, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,something really worthy of the\NCrystal Empire's admiration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You lit the torch\Nfor the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually, that\Nwasn't really--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't "worthy"\Nenough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For ponies' sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing you know, you'll be\Nasking to put on a rock concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Second place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We got silver!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations to\Nall our medalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the anthem of--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I shall do the\Nhonor of singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike? What are\Nyou doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how they always\Njust play the music?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know all the\Nwords to our anthem
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and will sing them for you\Nnow, loud and proud,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to the enjoyment of all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, um, the Cloudsdale\Nanthem, as sung by Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, the Cloudsdale anthem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They only play the anthem\Nfor the winners, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts are\Nfrom Cloudsdale!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know the words\Nto the Cloudsdale anthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sing for us, O Great{\i0}\N{\i1}and Honorable Spike{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Brave and Glorious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahem!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Oh we're the Wonderbolts! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And we're super-fast! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And we're from Cloudsdale{\i0}\N{\i1}which is a part of Equestria haha ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ that we like best and{\i0}\N{\i1}we're proud and we're fast ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and we like it because it{\i0}\N{\i1}really has nice trees ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and we love the town{\i0}\N{\i1}because it's so cool, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and we like to{\i0}\N{\i1}fly really fast ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and everything like that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Uh, I kind of wish this was{\i0}\N{\i1}over cause it isn't yet... ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ over.... Now...oh... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ we're the Wonderbolts! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And we're super-fast! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ And we're clear{\i0}\N{\i1}from Cloudsdale ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ We like it there{\i0}\N{\i1}because it's really nice ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and the trees are cool, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ and I hope this is over now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ and it keeps going on{\i0}\N{\i1}la la la... ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ and we really love the town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ So I wish that this{\i0}\N{\i1}song was over now ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Over now... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ Over now {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}NAILED IT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I got this\Nstuff to pack up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been moping in here\Nfor almost the entire Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And tonight's the\Nclosing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means we leave tomorrow.\NErgo the packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the Games conclude\Nas they always do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,with the Ice Archery finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ice archers, take your places!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad Ponyville doesn't have\Nany ice archers competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have\Nanyone to root for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville has 37 medals\Nand Cloudsdale 36,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so looks like we'll be medal\Nchamps of the Games anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But Cloudsdale has two\Nice archery finalists
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,down there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they both place, Cloudsdale{\i0}\N{\i1}wins the medal count.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying it all\Ncomes down to this one event?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh my gosh! Oh my gosh!{\i0}\N{\i1}Oh my gosh! Oh my gosh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Come take this\Nextra seat next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and freak out over\Nthe medal count.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Oh my gosh!\NOh my gosh! Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I was\Nlooking for Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to talk him into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have his\Nextra seat, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...Twi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spike? You here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. I'm super busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all this\Npacking left to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Crazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No more hiding out.\NYou're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, fine. I'll come. Can\NI at least wear these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't your\Naverage arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They freeze whatever part{\i0}\N{\i1}of the target they hit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoever encases their entire{\i0}\N{\i1}target in ice first wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep your eye on{\i0}\N{\i1}Number 7 from Cloudsdale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the favorite.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly Spike, I don't\Nsee why you're being
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,so hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I let everypony down. Twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You never let anypony down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so you have no idea\Nwhat that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? I've\Ntotally let ponies down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The torch got lit; the aerial\Nrelay teams got their medals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No harm no foul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we at least watch\Nfrom inside there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I'm ready to face\Ncrowds in the stands just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Steer it towards the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Away from the crowds!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony cut the\Ndisabling spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash! Fluttershy! MOVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to\Nthank you personally
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,for saving those ponies,\Nand the Games,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,O Great and Honorable Spike\Nthe Brave and Glorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.63,0:19:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be very proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw what needed\Nto be done and reacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happens\NI can breathe fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of you could do that,\Nyou'd have done the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for\Nbeing blunt, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not makin'\Na lick of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. I\Nthink I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep saying you\Nlet everypony down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we all keep\Nsaying you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who was disappointed\Nin you, Spike? You.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And only you can make\Nit right with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would that take, Spike?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Can\Nyou turn back time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause I'd sure like a do-over\Non that opening ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't turn back time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But would you do me\Nthe great honor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of lighting fireworks{\i0}\N{\i1}in my place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}at the closing{\i0}\N{\i1}ceremonies tonight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've saved the\NCrystal Empire. Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can\Nlight some fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to at\Nleast give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville won the medal count!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And only by one medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Wonder which\Nmedal that was?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it feel to have opened\Nthe best Equestria Games
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in Ponyville history, Squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably as good as it\Nfeels to close them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, it's kinda weird;{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how many times others\N{\i1}tell you you're great,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all the praise in{\i0}\N{\i1}the world means nothing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if you don't feel it inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes, to feel{\i0}\N{\i1}good about yourself,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you've got to let{\i0}\N{\i1}go of the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That way, when the time comes{\i0}\N{\i1}to let your greatness fly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'll be able to{\i0}\N{\i1}light up the whole sky.{\i0}
